### ðŸ”Œ Wiring Guide (for Arduino Uno)

| Component        | Arduino Pin | Notes                                      |
| ---------------- | ----------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **Flame Sensor** | D7          | DO â†’ D7, VCC â†’ 5V, GND â†’ GND               |
| **Gas Sensor**   | A0          | AO â†’ A0, VCC â†’ 5V, GND â†’ GND               |
| **Relay Module** | D4          | IN â†’ D4, VCC â†’ 5V (or external), GND â†’ GND |
| **IR Receiver**  | D2          | OUT â†’ D2, VCC â†’ 3.3V or 5V, GND â†’ GND      |

